00:02:38.330 --> 00:02:39.500
able to climb trees

00:02:39.500 --> 00:02:43.049
and now they're back to climb trees in a more natural setting

00:02:43.049 --> 00:02:47.390
this is not like anything we're able to do usually

00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:51.260
working on it you prevent additional research often

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:54.360
but you don't actually physically
see animals get out

